{"tid":367683,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"家母覺得一直對唔住個仔","createTime":"2017-08-21T02:38:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-25T16:36:36.000Z","uid":15739,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d325dfb1c543e048cae4bd276edf6fc1e8588899","tid":367683,"uid":15739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T02:38:24.000Z","msg":"講番個背景先，我有2個阿哥，有一個係同母異父既，因為家母改嫁比我爸爸。呢個阿哥係大陸住，本身有車有2層樓，有個醫生老婆，又有一仔一女，而且因為我地屋企親戚既關系，有份好工，算衣食無憂個種。但係從來無比過家母任何家用，只會係過年封個利是就算。<br />\n<br />\n問題就係，家母一直覺得欠左佢，無要求佢比家用，仲認為呢個阿哥讀唔好書、無一個好既童年係因為自己離婚既關係，但實情係佢出國讀書（英國留學），讀中學個陣掛住玩，所以讀唔到大學返左黎。之後個阿哥叫佢買咩就買咩，包括手機、甚至衫褲，阿哥對仔女出世以來，咩奶粉、尿片、dha、維他命、玩具，差唔多咩都係我媽買，但係，其實我媽無做野，d錢都係我爸既，只係我爸好人一直無過問，相反，我媽對我同我哥哥（同父同母既）就無咁好，細個個陣，我地買咩佢都話無錢叫我地問阿爸啦，到大個我地都有比家用，我留學日本，返pt都有比。講真，另外個阿哥佢已經算人生贏家，生父母都唔洗養，而且準備買第3層樓，媽媽仲覺得欠佢好多，要幫手養埋佢d仔女。。。而呢個阿哥又覺得理所當然咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想問有無巴絲有同樣情況？要點解決  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd8658be473b4ae8afab307c3c26f7448a6adee8","tid":367683,"uid":15739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T02:45:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eaa49b6489012914fbac109a69b522b81313d10","tid":367683,"uid":15739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T03:26:16.000Z","msg":"有無相同情況既巴絲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f6a8f27a9769c06d54d5c4c7f946edf16994afb","tid":367683,"uid":14088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T03:30:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無相同情況既巴絲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n除左停俾家用～偷偷地俾錢老豆<br />\n以外<br />\n都無咩好講"},{"pid":"7b4525587732da2252c4e947c6a9ac0327f28392","tid":367683,"uid":12111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T03:35:08.000Z","msg":"唔好再俾家用你老母咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c27fcf92e9196d51b98916b8cef7b5eb7210127","tid":367683,"uid":15739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T03:43:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無相同情況既巴絲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n除左停俾家用～偷偷地俾錢老豆<br />\n以外<br />\n都無咩好講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係停比既話，佢又係問爸爸攞，而且佢通常用credit card比，有10萬quota，碌完又係爸爸還"},{"pid":"2bd77c4dd552a032c5ec1407e371a1333d6a4dbe","tid":367683,"uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T03:48:53.000Z","msg":"睇佢個款都知佢唔想理你<br />\n你老豆對你好唔好先<br />\n唔好嘅話咪由佢幫你老母還卡數"},{"pid":"d96c0f09b0345b21b2adbb2c04b8192f7735ccf0","tid":367683,"uid":93816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T03:48:55.000Z","msg":"聽落你哥係唔抵幫，但中間嘅事又知幾多？"},{"pid":"a4665e79e7b511fecfd1dc5bd0c2c1789edf396c","tid":367683,"uid":15739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T03:58:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇佢個款都知佢唔想理你<br />\n你老豆對你好唔好先<br />\n唔好嘅話咪由佢幫你老母還卡數</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我爸爸好愛我媽，所以點都幫佢還既"},{"pid":"f6c5c8d957e482be77974db9087440ba94390907","tid":367683,"uid":15739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T04:03:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽落你哥係唔抵幫，但中間嘅事又知幾多？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢成日叫佢d仔女買咩就同嫲嫲講，之後我媽又好受呢套，咩都買，再遲d我驚我爸d身家都要分一半比佢（屋企中港2地都有d物業）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a096e52cd8ce0cd8f10b773ebed8e68bb75b158d","tid":367683,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T04:05:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d6a45dee112ea7aff0379971737ed13d82a44ad1","tid":367683,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T04:11:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2be7d3fcde624585e4335d9c92ec76288464a871","tid":367683,"uid":76908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T04:16:58.000Z","msg":"我做你男朋友，幫你氹掂你老豆，等佢比哂副身家你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a95775bac5d8d2269ce5b1d2a127d9cfb227a45c","tid":367683,"uid":15739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T05:29:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個年代唔比家用好正常<br />\n不過你老母要買嘢比佢地就多事咗啲囉<br />\n咁大個人自己搞掂啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都唔明，我記得上次佢地黎搵我日本玩，話無散紙，出去買支水、食個飯都要我比，我又傻真係比左，講真，我去日本讀有獎學金，但都有打工儲下錢唔想咩都問屋企，佢地一黎我又無左匹錢"},{"pid":"b6d951618a7d794dd3364463ed5cdc2520809e3f","tid":367683,"uid":15739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T05:30:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>聽落你哥係唔抵幫，但中間嘅事又知幾多？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢成日叫佢d仔女買咩就同嫲嫲講，之後我媽又好受呢套，咩都買，再遲d我驚我爸d身家都要分一半比佢（屋企中港2地都有d物業）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n早啲傾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n傾過，我媽成日話買少d，轉個頭又買好多野比佢地"},{"pid":"4867de7e3b2ff9980b93fc853a0c6d9e5e0abc73","tid":367683,"uid":15739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T05:32:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我做你男朋友，幫你氹掂你老豆，等佢比哂副身家你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔洗住啦，暫時唔想拍拖，比個意見我實際d"},{"pid":"4b557123b6fc4acf91ae53f45257d500e8bbc422","tid":367683,"uid":109050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T05:33:55.000Z","msg":"同我女友阿哥差唔多<br />\n佢阿媽又係覺得細個無好好教佢,無比佢讀好D書,讀到中學就無讀<br />\n依家廿幾歲人都唔洗比家用,生活雜費都係阿媽比,想食乜就叫阿媽買<br />\n但我條女就乜都要自己黎,仲要比埋家用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d145d09e7c55d5818a7e25539ff126a4470f5017","tid":367683,"uid":15739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T05:40:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同我女友阿哥差唔多<br />\n佢阿媽又係覺得細個無好好教佢,無比佢讀好D書,讀到中學就無讀<br />\n依家廿幾歲人都唔洗比家用,生活雜費都係阿媽比,想食乜就叫阿媽買<br />\n但我條女就乜都要自己黎,仲要比埋家用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你女朋友有無咩行動？<br />\n<br />\n我個case如果係同母同父既阿哥，我都無咩講，但佢係同母異父，而我媽無做野，一直靠爸爸支撐頭家，個阿哥從來無請過我爸爸食飯、無買過野比我爸，見到都只係叫聲uncle就算，我爸又好人，覺得無咩所謂，但我真係忍唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f56258067a3b3ca3968d51cd2ed06c363c92c4d","tid":367683,"uid":15739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T06:13:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d35c32c203b9fefae7b2cc04467688964796d90d","tid":367683,"uid":76941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T06:24:45.000Z","msg":"唔好比家用老母囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老豆想要咩食咩就直接買比佢同同佢食<br />\n對老豆好d 應該冇咁嬲"},{"pid":"62b75af0bd980b46c07c228127d27576bc38d601","tid":367683,"uid":15739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T08:36:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好比家用老母囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老豆想要咩食咩就直接買比佢同同佢食<br />\n對老豆好d 應該冇咁嬲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都想無咁嬲，我唔比我媽都會搵爸爸攞。。"},{"pid":"3c50a8b6b59591bc73c2550fa548f60b590f4ab1","tid":367683,"uid":76941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T13:57:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔好比家用老母囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老豆想要咩食咩就直接買比佢同同佢食<br />\n對老豆好d 應該冇咁嬲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都想無咁嬲，我唔比我媽都會搵爸爸攞。。</blockquote><br />\n我意思係直接大細超 做比你阿媽睇 你對阿爸超好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係對你唔好咋 老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1b375ed486e7a113fa006984db429924e898730","tid":367683,"uid":236401,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T16:36:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}